        "subject": "OSF-52 osp: add osp fid support",
        "message": "OSF-52 osp: add osp fid support\n\nAdd OST object FID support on OSP, OSP(MDT) requests FID sequence\nfrom OST, and OST requests super FID sequence from FID controller\nMDT0.\n\nFID will be used to track precreate objects, and add lov_seqs file\nto remember current seq of the precreation.\n\nDuring precreation, OSP will preallocate FIDs first, then send these\nFIDs to OST, and OST will precreate these objects with the FID.\n\nChange-Id: Ia8acca55efbcc7307e6f4f45623d9c3bdf67fed7\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
